# --- Local dev ---
# Leave both unset — `npm run dev` proxies /api → http://localhost:5000 (vite.config.js).

# --- Production on Vercel (pick ONE approach) ---
#
# A) Recommended: serverless proxy (no rebuild when API URL changes)
#    In Vercel → Environment Variables (Production + Preview), set:
#    BACKEND_URL=https://your-app.up.railway.app
#    The app posts to same-origin /api/contact; Vercel forwards to your Express API.
#
# B) Bake API URL into the client build instead:
#    VITE_API_URL=https://your-app.up.railway.app
#
# BACKEND_URL=
# VITE_API_URL=
